WEBVTT

01:43:22.149 --> 01:43:23.233
But I was wrong.

01:43:24.441 --> 01:43:26.108
She broke down crying,

01:43:26.441 --> 01:43:28.149
saying I had never
done anything for her

01:43:28.274 --> 01:43:29.774
and that I never stood by her.

01:43:30.858 --> 01:43:33.024
After that, she slowly stopped
talking to me.

01:43:33.774 --> 01:43:34.816
She stopped going out.
